metadata.name: The Plan EP01: Approaching
metadata.description:
The Plan is a series of images that tells a Sci-Fi story involving spaceships, alien planets and big dystopian cities. 

EP 01: Approaching

A strange communication lost in the space leads us to a mysterious rocky planet with hostile weather.

Could this signal be what we were waiting for? It looks like hope is not lost after all...

-------------------------------------------------------------

Blender, Substance Painter and Photoshop

4803x2160pixels 300ppi 32Bits
